Interface Summary
ShapeCollection Container for Shapes with the ability to draw them.
 

Class Summary

Zone Represents a zone that the rat can enter.
ZonesCollection Collection of zones, with the facilities to add, remove and get zones in an easy way.
ZonesModule Manages zones counters (entrance counters, central time, etc..).
ZonesModuleConfigs Configuration class for the zones module.
ZonesModuleData Data of the Zones Module.
ZonesModuleGUI GUI class for the ZonesModule.
 

Enum Summary
